response.overview: Having met on a train, a smooth-talking psychotic socialite shares his theory on how two complete strangers can get away with murder to an amateur tennis player — a theory he plans to test out.
response.tagline: It starts with a shriek of a train whistle... and ends with shrieking excitement!
response.title: Strangers on a Train
